descriptionHtml:
[size=6]                                                     [color=#00ff00]AVENFELL[/color][/size]                                                                                                                         [color=#00ff00][size=5]Players home.[/size][/color]                  

To get to AVENFELL open map see pics for location then teleport there. 

To get a good idea of AVENFELL look throught the pics.   AVENFELL has manniquins, weapon racks, soil for planting, tanning rack forge smelter ETC. 

I have tested the navmesh with a follower and encountered no problems.

[color=#ff7700][size=5]Requirements:[/size][/color]   Dawnguard.Hearthfire.Dragonborn.

[size=5][color=#ff7700]Installation:[/color] [/size]         Just download with Nexus mod manger, Mod organizer or manual,if you want to install it manually,                                                                                                            then you have to extract it into your data file for Skyrim.

[size=5][color=#ff7700]Unistallation:[/color] [/size]      Just untick in mod manger or mod organzier or delete the files you manually installed.


[color=#00ff00][size=5]CREDITS:                  Many thanks to.     [/size][/color][color=#00ff00][size=5]                                                             [/size][/color][color=#00ff00][size=5]

[/size][/color][color=#00ff00][size=5]                                  "tamira for resorces"


[/size][/color]There are 3 guards one at the gate to AVENFELL, 2 inside in the throne room.If you get the black face bug on the guards it will not be due to this mod, i took a long time to learn and make sure this would not happen, so please check your mod list to make sure one of your mods is not altering the vanila npcs in this mod.

The weapons in the main entrance don,t come with this mod,  there is a room for vampires you just need to find it.


I hope you enjoy the home.

Thank You.
